{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/posts/datacon-2019/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Code Me, dsewnr","author":"dsewnr"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"3de2b65a-5026-5881-8c05-f16130d2db8a","excerpt":"9/6 有幸與一位同事和一位前同事去參加 DataCon.TW 201…","html":"<p>9/6 有幸與一位同事和一位前同事去參加 DataCon.TW 2019</p>\n<!--more-->\n<p>在我們還是同事的時候就一起報名了，雖然我不是資料工程專業人員…</p>\n<p>上午是共同議程加贊助商時段交錯，下午則分應用案例、營運者及開發者三軌，我是選擇開發者。</p>\n<p>這次最讓我印象深刻的是國泰金控在資料工程領域走的好前面喔！令人非常意外！</p>\n<p>還有 Cloudera 的講者在解析市面上流行的資料工程工具的趨勢也是蠻棒的。</p>\n<p>講者在 Apache Software Foundation 開源的貢獻非常令人激賞！</p>\n<p>當然還聽到很多其他非常不錯的分享，希望明年還有機會參加 😀</p>\n<h3>DataCon.TW 2019</h3>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 720px;\"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 133.33333333333331%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"datacon 2019\"\n        title=\"datacon 2019\"\n        src=\"/static/91b050c6187c2abc60fe40cf6d5b6bbb/80e3c/datacon-2019.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/91b050c6187c2abc60fe40cf6d5b6bbb/4ec73/datacon-2019.jpg 180w,\n/static/91b050c6187c2abc60fe40cf6d5b6bbb/158ba/datacon-2019.jpg 360w,\n/static/91b050c6187c2abc60fe40cf6d5b6bbb/80e3c/datacon-2019.jpg 720w,\n/static/91b050c6187c2abc60fe40cf6d5b6bbb/6a068/datacon-2019.jpg 960w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 720px) 100vw, 720px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>","frontmatter":{"title":"DataCon.TW 2019","date":"September 26, 2019"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/datacon-2019/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/enjoy-121/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Ergohuman Enjoy 121 企業版開箱，新椅子來囉~"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/pycon-taiwan-2019/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"PyCon Taiwan 2019"}}}}}